                Explore trusted lending partners offering competitive rates for business loans, equipment financing, and lines of credit.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a href="#" class="text-sm text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">Compare Lenders ‚Üí</a>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">SBA Loans ‚Üí</a>
